  dmdDetailFilterClose() (in lab-created-diamonds.js, called after every
  add-to-cart) does document.querySelector(".dmd-detail-filter").innerHTML = '',
  not optionally-chained. This page has no drawer, so this inert element
  just keeps that call from throwing.
